	<li Class="ScenPart_GameStartDialog">
				<def>GameStartDialog</def>
				<text>Within hours of waking up from crypto-sleep, the mothership spits your capsules right out to this new Earth. As you enter the atmosphere, the voice of your commanding officer erupts from the intercom : "Good morning soldiers ! Today, you can be proud of yourself, as you will accomplish the destiny of our glorious nation ! In few minutes you will walk the surface of this unknown world with one single goal in mind : to bring progress and democracy ! Secure the resources you need and mark the first steps of a New American Nation ! Be advised that intelligence reports scattered human-like inhabitants with oblivious signs of hostility. The use of lethal force is authorized should you encounter any resistance. Rampant communist infiltration must be considered and is currently under investigation. Ground forces are already operational in this sector and will assist on demand. Mothership out."</text>
